{"tid":1121391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香水？有無人鍾意香水？又有無人好唔鍾意香水？","createTime":"2019-04-23T09:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T10:20:32.000Z","uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5ba7594959a4e465822b3ad91457b4453766d0","tid":1121391,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"讀書見到呢段：<br />\n<br />\n<em>你要像老派的紳士那樣，穿上襯衫，把鬍子刮乾淨，穿上灰色的開襟毛衣還有帆船鞋，到我家來接我。把你的鉚釘皮衣丟掉，一輩子不要穿它。<ins>不要用麝香或柑橘或任何氣味的古龍水，我想聞到你剛洗過澡的香皂以及洗髮精。</ins>因為幾個小時之後，我要就著那味道上床入睡。</em><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;李維菁，《老派約會之必要》<br />\n<br />\n有無人特登為左陣香皂同洗頭水味，而唔用香水？<br />\n<br />\n有咩沐浴露同洗頭水可以香好耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a906ac4d56ec653a37844693c99083beaa31e3","tid":1121391,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb25ef8965e94bd34cf0288e630206393fa07ae7","tid":1121391,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5a906ac4d56ec653a37844693c99083beaa31e3","tid":1121391,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得靚仔靚女用咩都香，其他就&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3548d10892447b2e27b1510564a81300d08da147","tid":1121391,"uid":103172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb25ef8965e94bd34cf0288e630206393fa07ae7","tid":1121391,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5a906ac4d56ec653a37844693c99083beaa31e3","tid":1121391,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得靚仔靚女用咩都香，其他就&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"有啲味噴太重手會好俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgm